  <body dur="03:21.860">
    <div begin="00:23.930" end="03:21.860">
      <p begin="00:23.930" end="00:33.510" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:23.930" end="00:25.250">旅</span><span begin="00:25.250" end="00:25.710">は</span><span begin="00:25.850" end="00:27.080">続</span><span begin="00:27.150" end="00:27.560">い</span><span begin="00:27.760" end="00:28.280">て</span><span begin="00:28.380" end="00:28.840">い</span><span begin="00:29.000" end="00:29.680">く</span> <span begin="00:31.350" end="00:31.470">背</span><span begin="00:31.540" end="00:31.810">負</span><span begin="00:31.810" end="00:32.030">う</span><span begin="00:32.030" end="00:32.650">足</span><span begin="00:32.650" end="00:33.510">跡</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">旅途仍在继续 背负着留下的足迹</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">旅途仍在繼續 背負著留下的足跡</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The journey continues footprints borne on my back</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">여행은 계속되어 가, 짊어진 발자국</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le voyage continue en portant le fardeau de nos empreintes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El viaje continúa cargando con las huellas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Reise geht weiter die Fußspuren die wir auf dem Rücken tragen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A jornada continua as pegadas que carrego</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Путешествие продолжается следы что я несу за спиной</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il viaggio continua le orme che mi porto addosso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tabi wa tsuzuite iku seou ashiato</span></p>
      <p begin="00:33.910" end="00:43.680" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:33.910" end="00:35.320">再</span><span begin="00:35.370" end="00:35.900">び</span><span begin="00:35.970" end="00:37.550">瞳</span><span begin="00:37.840" end="00:38.440">閉</span><span begin="00:38.500" end="00:38.960">じ</span><span begin="00:38.990" end="00:40.880">る</span> <span begin="00:41.450" end="00:41.740">再</span><span begin="00:41.790" end="00:42.110">会</span><span begin="00:42.110" end="00:42.360">を</span><span begin="00:42.440" end="00:42.940">願</span><span begin="00:42.940" end="00:43.070">っ</span><span begin="00:43.070" end="00:43.680">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">再次闭上双眼 祈愿着能够重逢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">再次閉上雙眼 祈願著能夠重逢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Closing my eyes again wishing for a reunion</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">다시 눈을 감아, 재회를 바라며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ferme à nouveau les yeux en espérant des retrouvailles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Vuelvo a cerrar los ojos deseando un reencuentro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich schließe wieder die Augen und hoffe auf ein Wiedersehen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Fecho os olhos novamente desejando um reencontro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Вновь закрываю глаза желая о новой встрече</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Chiudo di nuovo gli occhi sperando in un ricongiungimento</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Futatabi hitomi tojiru saikai o negatte</span></p>
      <p begin="00:44.170" end="00:48.970" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:44.170" end="00:44.720">ねえ</span><span begin="00:44.720" end="00:44.750">、</span><span begin="00:45.420" end="00:46.010">ねえ</span><span begin="00:46.010" end="00:46.040">、</span><span begin="00:46.510" end="00:47.010">掴</span><span begin="00:47.010" end="00:47.170">ん</span><span begin="00:47.170" end="00:47.370">だ</span><span begin="00:47.460" end="00:47.650">つ</span><span begin="00:47.800" end="00:48.120">も</span><span begin="00:48.120" end="00:48.350">り</span><span begin="00:48.380" end="00:48.470">が</span><span begin="00:48.570" end="00:48.700">ま</span><span begin="00:48.760" end="00:48.970">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">呐 呐 明明以为已经抓住 却又</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">吶 吶 明明以為已經抓住 卻又</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Hey, hey, I thought I grasped it but again</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">있지, 있지, 붙잡았다고 생각했는데 또다시</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dis dis je croyais l'avoir saisi mais encore une fois</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Oye, oye, creí haberlo atrapado pero otra vez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hey hey ich dachte ich hätte es gegriffen doch schon wieder</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ei, ei, achei que tinha agarrado mas de novo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Эй эй думала что ухватилась но снова</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ehi ehi pensavo di averlo afferrato e invece</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nee, nee, tsukanda tsumori ga mata</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:44.730" end="00:46.660"><span begin="00:44.730" end="00:45.360">(ねえ</span><span begin="00:45.360" end="00:45.390">、</span><span begin="00:46.030" end="00:46.660">ねえ)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">呐 呐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">吶 吶</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Hey, hey</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">있지, 있지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dis dis</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Oye, oye</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hey hey</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ei, ei</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Эй эй</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ehi ehi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nee, nee</span></span></p>
      <p begin="00:49.230" end="00:51.140" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:49.230" end="00:49.810">明</span><span begin="00:50.470" end="00:51.140">滅</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">明灭</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">明滅</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Flickering</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">명멸</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Scintillement</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Parpadeo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Flackern</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tremeluzir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мерцание</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sfarfallio</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Meimetsu</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:49.810" end="00:50.380"><span begin="00:49.810" end="00:50.380">(めい)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">明</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">明</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Flic</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">명...</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Scin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Par</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Fla-</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мер</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sfa</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mei</span></span></p>
      <p begin="00:51.440" end="00:56.560" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:51.440" end="00:52.620">幻</span><span begin="00:52.680" end="00:52.950">だ</span><span begin="00:53.020" end="00:53.320">け</span> <span begin="00:53.660" end="00:54.230">憶</span><span begin="00:54.300" end="00:54.530">え</span><span begin="00:54.610" end="00:54.870">て</span><span begin="00:54.920" end="00:55.240">い</span><span begin="00:55.240" end="00:55.480">る</span><span begin="00:55.580" end="00:56.560">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">唯有幻影 依然铭记于心哦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">唯有幻影 依然銘記於心哦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I only remember the illusion</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">환상만을 기억하고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne me souviens que des illusions</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Solo recuerdo las ilusiones</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Nur an die Illusionen erinnere ich mich</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Só me lembro de ilusões</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я помню лишь иллюзии</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ricordo soltanto le illusioni</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Maboroshi dake oboete iru yo</span></p>
      <p begin="00:57.390" end="01:02.100" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:57.390" end="00:57.910">な</span><span begin="00:57.910" end="00:58.040">ん</span><span begin="00:58.040" end="00:58.340">で</span><span begin="00:58.660" end="00:59.330">僕</span><span begin="00:59.330" end="00:59.900">ら</span><span begin="00:59.940" end="01:00.240">は</span><span begin="01:00.580" end="01:00.740">自</span><span begin="01:00.770" end="01:01.010">分</span><span begin="01:01.070" end="01:01.280">勝</span><span begin="01:01.390" end="01:01.610">手</span><span begin="01:01.700" end="01:02.100">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">为什么我们总是 自私自利地</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">為什麼我們總是 自私自利地</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Why do we take such selfish</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어째서 우리는 이기적인</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pourquoi brandissons-nous notre amour égoïste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Por qué nosotras tan egoístas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Warum schwingen wir nur unsere egoistische</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Por que nós, de forma tão egoísta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Почему же мы размахивая</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Perché noi in modo egoistico</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nande bokura wa jibungatte na</span></p>
      <p begin="01:02.440" end="01:07.690" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="01:02.440" end="01:03.130">愛</span><span begin="01:03.130" end="01:03.400">を</span><span begin="01:03.730" end="01:04.080">振</span><span begin="01:04.080" end="01:04.320">り</span><span begin="01:04.380" end="01:04.930">か</span><span begin="01:05.000" end="01:05.300">ざ</span><span begin="01:05.300" end="01:05.400">し</span><span begin="01:05.640" end="01:06.000">傷</span><span begin="01:06.100" end="01:06.350">つ</span><span begin="01:06.430" end="01:06.750">け</span><span begin="01:06.750" end="01:06.960">合</span><span begin="01:06.960" end="01:07.050">う</span><span begin="01:07.080" end="01:07.660">の</span><span begin="01:07.660" end="01:07.690">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">挥舞着爱意 互相伤害呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">揮舞著愛意 互相傷害呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Love to brandish and hurt each other?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">사랑을 휘두르며 서로를 상처 입히는 걸까?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et nous blessons-nous mutuellement ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Blandimos el amor y nos lastimamos mutuamente?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Liebe umher und verletzen einander?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Empunhamos o amor e machucamos umas às outras?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Своей эгоистичной любовью раним друг друга</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Brandiamo l'amore e ci feriamo a vicenda</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ai o furikazashi kizutsukeau no?</span></p>
      <p begin="01:08.020" end="01:12.360" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="01:08.020" end="01:08.090">ま</span><span begin="01:08.170" end="01:08.580">た</span><span begin="01:08.630" end="01:09.010">一</span><span begin="01:09.010" end="01:09.090">つ</span> <span begin="01:09.300" end="01:09.380">ま</span><span begin="01:09.450" end="01:09.870">た</span><span begin="01:09.910" end="01:10.270">一</span><span begin="01:10.270" end="01:10.350">つ</span> <span begin="01:10.560" end="01:11.160">灯</span><span begin="01:11.160" end="01:11.260">が</span><span begin="01:11.340" end="01:11.800">消</span><span begin="01:11.800" end="01:11.890">え</span><span begin="01:11.960" end="01:12.360">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">又一盏 又一盏 灯火熄灭了</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">又一盞 又一盞 燈火熄滅了</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">One by one again and again the lights went out</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">또 하나, 또 하나 등불이 꺼졌어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Encore une encore une une lumière s'est éteinte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Se apagó una luz y luego otra</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wieder eins und noch eins ein Licht ist erloschen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mais uma mais uma luz se apagou</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Еще один и еще один свет погас</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ancora una ancora una una luce si è spenta</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mata hitotsu mata hitotsu akari ga kieta</span></p>
      <p begin="01:12.580" end="01:17.880" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="01:12.580" end="01:13.100">な</span><span begin="01:13.100" end="01:13.220">ん</span><span begin="01:13.220" end="01:13.480">て</span><span begin="01:13.840" end="01:14.360">愛</span><span begin="01:14.470" end="01:14.890">し</span><span begin="01:14.960" end="01:15.060">く</span><span begin="01:15.130" end="01:15.350">て</span><span begin="01:15.710" end="01:16.120">愚</span><span begin="01:16.210" end="01:16.520">か</span><span begin="01:16.550" end="01:16.760">な</span><span begin="01:16.850" end="01:17.880">の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">多么惹人怜爱 却又多么愚蠢啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">多麼惹人憐愛 卻又多麼愚蠢啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">How dear and foolish it is</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">얼마나 사랑스럽고 어리석은지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Comme c'est attachant et stupide</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Qué adorables y tontas somos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wie liebenswert und doch so töricht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Como somos amáveis e tolas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Как же это мило и как глупо</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quanto siamo preziosi e sciocchi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nante itoshikute oroka na no</span></p>
      <p begin="01:18.270" end="01:23.160" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="01:18.270" end="01:18.670">声</span><span begin="01:18.770" end="01:18.970">無</span><span begin="01:19.070" end="01:19.320">き</span><span begin="01:19.400" end="01:19.710">声</span><span begin="01:19.710" end="01:19.920">を</span><span begin="01:20.030" end="01:20.310">聞</span><span begin="01:20.360" end="01:20.440">か</span><span begin="01:20.490" end="01:20.590">せ</span><span begin="01:20.670" end="01:23.160">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">让我听见那无声的声音吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">讓我聽見那無聲的聲音吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Let me hear the voiceless voice</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">소리 없는 목소리를 들려줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Laisse-moi entendre cette voix sans voix</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Déjame escuchar tu voz sin voz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lass mich deine stimmlose Stimme hören</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Deixe-me ouvir a voz sem voz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Дай мне услышать беззвучный голос</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Fammi sentire la tua voce senza voce</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Koenaki koe o kikasete</span></p>
      <p begin="01:30.900" end="01:35.660" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="01:30.900" end="01:31.830">届</span><span begin="01:31.830" end="01:32.040">い</span><span begin="01:32.180" end="01:32.990">て</span><span begin="01:33.460" end="01:33.920">い</span><span begin="01:33.960" end="01:34.320">る</span><span begin="01:34.360" end="01:34.550">で</span><span begin="01:34.680" end="01:35.660">しょ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">已经传达到了吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">已經傳達到了吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It's reaching you right</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">닿고 있겠지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ça t'est parvenu n'est-ce pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Te está llegando verdad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es hat dich doch erreicht oder</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Está te alcançando, não está</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ведь он доходит до тебя не так ли</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ti sta raggiungendo vero</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Todoite iru desho</span></p>
      <p begin="01:36.280" end="01:40.390" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="01:36.280" end="01:36.600">未</span><span begin="01:36.600" end="01:37.480">来</span><span begin="01:37.560" end="01:37.910">の</span><span begin="01:38.450" end="01:39.650">導</span><span begin="01:39.720" end="01:40.390">が</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">未来的指引</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">未來的指引</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The guidance of the future</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">미래의 이정표가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La guidance de l'avenir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La guía hacia el futuro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Führung der Zukunft</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O guia para o futuro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Путеводный свет будущего</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La guida verso il futuro</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mirai no michibiki ga</span></p>
      <p begin="01:40.840" end="01:45.570" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="01:40.840" end="01:41.020">揺</span><span begin="01:41.020" end="01:41.170">ら</span><span begin="01:41.170" end="01:41.290">い</span><span begin="01:41.350" end="01:41.830">で</span> <span begin="01:42.110" end="01:42.250">ぼ</span><span begin="01:42.250" end="01:42.360">や</span><span begin="01:42.410" end="01:42.510">け</span><span begin="01:42.610" end="01:43.120">て</span> <span begin="01:43.390" end="01:43.700">滲</span><span begin="01:43.700" end="01:43.910">ん</span><span begin="01:43.910" end="01:44.420">で</span> <span begin="01:44.630" end="01:44.940">溢</span><span begin="01:44.940" end="01:45.060">れ</span><span begin="01:45.130" end="01:45.570">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">摇曳着 模糊着 渗漏着 满溢着</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">搖曳著 模糊著 滲漏著 滿溢著</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Swaying blurring bleeding overflowing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">흔들리고 흐릿해지고 번지고 흘러넘쳐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Vacille se brouille s'estompe et déborde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tiembla se vuelve borrosa se desdibuja se desborda</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Schwankt verschwimmt verschmiert und fließt über</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Balançando embaçando borrando transbordando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Колеблется размывается расплывается переполняется</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Oscilla si sfoca si sfuma e trabocca</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Yuraide boyakete nijinde afurete</span></p>
      <p begin="01:45.870" end="01:49.780" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="01:45.870" end="01:46.070">そ</span><span begin="01:46.070" end="01:46.200">れ</span><span begin="01:46.230" end="01:46.330">で</span><span begin="01:46.390" end="01:46.910">も</span> <span begin="01:47.180" end="01:47.530">堪</span><span begin="01:47.530" end="01:47.590">え</span><span begin="01:47.660" end="01:48.180">て</span><span begin="01:48.180" end="01:48.230">い</span><span begin="01:48.290" end="01:48.410">く</span><span begin="01:48.450" end="01:49.780">の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">尽管如此 依然要强忍着走下去吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">儘管如此 依然要強忍著走下去嗎</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even so I will endure it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그럼에도 견뎌나가는 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Malgré tout je continuerai à l'endurer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aun así lo sigo soportando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und dennoch ertrage ich es weiter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo assim continuo suportando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Но я всё равно продолжаю терпеть</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Eppure continuo a sopportare</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Soredemo koraete iku no</span></p>
      <p begin="01:50.470" end="01:55.180" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:50.470" end="01:51.000">な</span><span begin="01:51.000" end="01:51.110">ん</span><span begin="01:51.110" end="01:51.410">で</span><span begin="01:51.760" end="01:52.390">僕</span><span begin="01:52.390" end="01:52.960">ら</span><span begin="01:53.010" end="01:53.330">は</span><span begin="01:53.630" end="01:53.780">自</span><span begin="01:53.800" end="01:54.050">分</span><span begin="01:54.100" end="01:54.330">勝</span><span begin="01:54.440" end="01:54.660">手</span><span begin="01:54.760" end="01:55.180">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">为什么我们总是 自私自利地</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">為什麼我們總是 自私自利地</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Why do we take such selfish</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어째서 우리는 이기적인</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pourquoi brandissons-nous notre amour égoïste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Por qué nosotras tan egoístas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Warum schwingen wir nur unsere egoistische</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Por que nós, de forma tão egoísta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Почему же мы размахивая</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Perché noi in modo egoistico</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nande bokura wa jibungatte na</span></p>
      <p begin="01:55.470" end="02:00.760" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:55.470" end="01:56.190">愛</span><span begin="01:56.190" end="01:56.460">を</span><span begin="01:56.780" end="01:57.120">振</span><span begin="01:57.120" end="01:57.350">り</span><span begin="01:57.420" end="01:57.970">か</span><span begin="01:58.040" end="01:58.360">ざ</span><span begin="01:58.360" end="01:58.460">し</span><span begin="01:58.690" end="01:59.070">傷</span><span begin="01:59.160" end="01:59.400">つ</span><span begin="01:59.500" end="01:59.810">け</span><span begin="01:59.810" end="02:00.040">合</span><span begin="02:00.040" end="02:00.140">う</span><span begin="02:00.140" end="02:00.730">の</span><span begin="02:00.730" end="02:00.760">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">挥舞着爱意 互相伤害呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">揮舞著愛意 互相傷害呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Love to brandish and hurt each other?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">사랑을 휘두르며 서로를 상처 입히는 걸까?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et nous blessons-nous mutuellement ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Blandimos el amor y nos lastimamos mutuamente?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Liebe umher und verletzen einander?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Empunhamos o amor e machucamos umas às outras?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Своей эгоистичной любовью раним друг друга</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Brandiamo l'amore e ci feriamo a vicenda</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ai o furikazashi kizutsukeau no?</span></p>
      <p begin="02:01.040" end="02:05.340" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="02:01.040" end="02:01.560">優</span><span begin="02:01.560" end="02:01.650">し</span><span begin="02:01.650" end="02:01.830">さ</span><span begin="02:01.860" end="02:02.120">で</span><span begin="02:02.330" end="02:02.420">世</span><span begin="02:02.500" end="02:03.120">界</span><span begin="02:03.120" end="02:03.400">が</span><span begin="02:03.570" end="02:04.210">救</span><span begin="02:04.210" end="02:04.400">わ</span><span begin="02:04.400" end="02:04.740">れ</span><span begin="02:04.740" end="02:04.830">る</span><span begin="02:04.880" end="02:05.040">な</span><span begin="02:05.040" end="02:05.340">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">若是温柔 就能拯救这个世界</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">若是溫柔 就能拯救這個世界</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">If the world can be saved by kindness</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">다정함으로 세상이 구원받을 수 있다면</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Si la gentillesse pouvait sauver le monde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si el mundo se salva con amabilidad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn die Welt durch Freundlichkeit gerettet werden kann</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se a bondade pode salvar o mundo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Если доброта способна спасти мир</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se il mondo può essere salvato dalla gentilezza</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Yasashisa de sekai ga sukuwareru nara</span></p>
      <p begin="02:05.630" end="02:10.940" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="02:05.630" end="02:05.970">ど</span><span begin="02:05.970" end="02:06.160">う</span><span begin="02:06.160" end="02:06.300">し</span><span begin="02:06.300" end="02:06.540">て</span><span begin="02:06.880" end="02:07.440">今</span> <span begin="02:07.540" end="02:08.180">僕</span><span begin="02:08.180" end="02:08.430">は</span><span begin="02:08.680" end="02:08.900">苦</span><span begin="02:08.960" end="02:09.230">し</span><span begin="02:09.310" end="02:09.510">い</span><span begin="02:09.510" end="02:09.610">ん</span><span begin="02:09.610" end="02:09.930">だ</span><span begin="02:09.930" end="02:10.170">ろ</span><span begin="02:10.170" end="02:10.940">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">为什么此刻 我还会感到如此痛苦呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">為什麼此刻 我還會感到如此痛苦呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Why am I suffering right now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어째서 지금 나는 이토록 괴로운 걸까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pourquoi suis-je en train de souffrir autant maintenant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Por qué estoy sufriendo tanto ahora mismo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Warum leide ich dann jetzt so sehr</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Por que eu estou sofrendo agora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">То почему же мне сейчас так больно</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Perché ora io sto soffrendo così</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Doushite ima boku wa kurushiin darou</span></p>
      <p begin="02:11.300" end="02:15.650" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="02:11.300" end="02:11.690">声</span><span begin="02:11.810" end="02:12.030">無</span><span begin="02:12.120" end="02:12.370">き</span><span begin="02:12.440" end="02:12.760">声</span><span begin="02:12.760" end="02:13.000">よ</span><span begin="02:13.070" end="02:13.630">響</span><span begin="02:13.630" end="02:13.850">い</span><span begin="02:14.470" end="02:15.650">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无声的声音啊 回荡起来吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無聲的聲音啊 迴盪起來吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Voiceless voice echo out</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">소리 없는 목소리여 울려 퍼져라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Que cette voix sans voix résonne</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Que resuene la voz sin voz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Oh stimmlose Stimme halle wider</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ó voz sem voz, ressoe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">О беззвучный голос звучи эхом</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Risuona o voce senza voce</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Koenaki koe yo hibiite</span></p>
      <p begin="02:26.470" end="02:31.340" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="02:26.470" end="02:27.110">ねえ</span><span begin="02:27.110" end="02:27.140">、</span><span begin="02:27.780" end="02:28.380">ねえ</span><span begin="02:28.380" end="02:28.410">、</span><span begin="02:28.840" end="02:28.930">失</span><span begin="02:28.990" end="02:29.070">く</span><span begin="02:29.150" end="02:29.380">し</span><span begin="02:29.480" end="02:29.690">た</span><span begin="02:29.800" end="02:29.990">つ</span><span begin="02:30.140" end="02:30.440">も</span><span begin="02:30.480" end="02:30.710">り</span><span begin="02:30.750" end="02:30.860">が</span><span begin="02:30.940" end="02:31.060">ま</span><span begin="02:31.100" end="02:31.340">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">呐 呐 明明以为已经失去 却还</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">吶 吶 明明以為已經失去 卻還</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Hey, hey, I thought I lost it but still</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">있지, 있지, 잃어버렸다고 생각했는데 아직</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dis dis je croyais l'avoir perdu mais encore</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Oye, oye, creí haberlo perdido pero aún</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hey hey ich dachte ich hätte es verloren doch noch immer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ei, ei, achei que tinha perdido mas ainda</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Эй эй думала что потеряла но всё ещё</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ehi ehi pensavo di averlo perso e invece</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nee, nee, nakushita tsumori ga mada</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="02:27.080" end="02:28.970"><span begin="02:27.080" end="02:27.630">(ねえ</span><span begin="02:27.630" end="02:27.660">、</span><span begin="02:28.370" end="02:28.970">ねえ)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">呐 呐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">吶 吶</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Hey, hey</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">있지, 있지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dis dis</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Oye, oye</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hey hey</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ei, ei</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Эй эй</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ehi ehi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nee, nee</span></span></p>
      <p begin="02:31.570" end="02:33.760" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="02:31.570" end="02:32.210">明</span><span begin="02:32.800" end="02:33.760">滅</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">明灭</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">明滅</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Flickering</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">명멸</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Scintillement</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Parpadeo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Flackern</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tremeluzir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мерцание</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sfarfallio</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Meimetsu</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="02:32.140" end="02:32.710"><span begin="02:32.140" end="02:32.710">(めい)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">明</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">明</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Flic</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">명...</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Scin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Par</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Fla-</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мер</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sfa</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mei</span></span></p>
      <p begin="02:35.920" end="02:40.640" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="02:35.920" end="02:36.190">書</span><span begin="02:36.270" end="02:36.450">き</span><span begin="02:36.610" end="02:37.460">進</span><span begin="02:37.600" end="02:37.740">め</span><span begin="02:37.890" end="02:38.460">て</span><span begin="02:38.490" end="02:38.750">る</span><span begin="02:39.120" end="02:39.310">手</span><span begin="02:39.310" end="02:39.490">が</span><span begin="02:39.620" end="02:39.810">止</span><span begin="02:39.950" end="02:40.150">ま</span><span begin="02:40.260" end="02:40.640">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">不断书写着的手 停了下来</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">不斷書寫著的手 停了下來</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The hand that keeps writing stops</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">글을 써 내려가던 손이 멈춰</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ma main qui continuait d'écrire s'arrête</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La mano con la que sigo escribiendo se detiene</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Hand die weiterschreibt hält inne</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A mão que continuava escrevendo para</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Рука продолжающая писать замирает</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La mano che continua a scrivere si ferma</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kakisusumeteru te ga tomaru</span></p>
      <p begin="02:41.000" end="02:43.850" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="02:41.000" end="02:41.340">ど</span><span begin="02:41.340" end="02:41.480">う</span><span begin="02:41.640" end="02:41.960">か</span><span begin="02:42.300" end="02:42.460">い</span><span begin="02:42.590" end="02:42.790">か</span><span begin="02:42.950" end="02:43.270">な</span><span begin="02:43.270" end="02:43.440">い</span><span begin="02:43.570" end="02:43.850">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">求求你不要走</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">求求你不要走</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Please don't go</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">제발 가지 말아 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je t'en prie ne pars pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Por favor no te vayas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bitte geh nicht fort</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Por favor, não vá</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Прошу не уходи</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ti prego non te ne andare</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Douka ikanaide</span></p>
      <p begin="02:46.030" end="02:50.740" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="02:46.030" end="02:46.610">な</span><span begin="02:46.610" end="02:46.680">ん</span><span begin="02:46.680" end="02:47.010">で</span><span begin="02:47.340" end="02:47.960">僕</span><span begin="02:47.960" end="02:48.530">ら</span><span begin="02:48.590" end="02:48.890">は</span><span begin="02:49.190" end="02:49.320">自</span><span begin="02:49.370" end="02:49.610">分</span><span begin="02:49.660" end="02:49.890">勝</span><span begin="02:50.000" end="02:50.200">手</span><span begin="02:50.320" end="02:50.740">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">为什么我们总是 自私自利地</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">為什麼我們總是 自私自利地</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Why do we take such selfish</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어째서 우리는 이기적인</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pourquoi brandissons-nous notre amour égoïste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Por qué nosotras tan egoístas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Warum schwingen wir nur unsere egoistische</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Por que nós, de forma tão egoísta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Почему же мы размахивая</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Perché noi in modo egoistico</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nande bokura wa jibungatte na</span></p>
      <p begin="02:51.080" end="02:56.410" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L25"><span begin="02:51.080" end="02:51.760">愛</span><span begin="02:51.760" end="02:52.040">を</span><span begin="02:52.360" end="02:52.700">振</span><span begin="02:52.700" end="02:52.910">り</span><span begin="02:53.010" end="02:53.570">か</span><span begin="02:53.640" end="02:53.950">ざ</span><span begin="02:53.950" end="02:54.050">し</span><span begin="02:54.280" end="02:54.660">傷</span><span begin="02:54.740" end="02:55.000">つ</span><span begin="02:55.080" end="02:55.410">け</span><span begin="02:55.410" end="02:55.630">合</span><span begin="02:55.630" end="02:55.740">う</span><span begin="02:55.740" end="02:56.380">の</span><span begin="02:56.380" end="02:56.410">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">挥舞着爱意 互相伤害呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">揮舞著愛意 互相傷害呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Love to brandish and hurt each other?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">사랑을 휘두르며 서로를 상처 입히는 걸까?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et nous blessons-nous mutuellement ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Blandimos el amor y nos lastimamos mutuamente?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Liebe umher und verletzen einander?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Empunhamos o amor e machucamos umas às outras?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Своей эгоистичной любовью раним друг друга</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Brandiamo l'amore e ci feriamo a vicenda</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ai o furikazashi kizutsukeau no?</span></p>
      <p begin="02:56.650" end="03:00.930" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L26"><span begin="02:56.650" end="02:56.700">ま</span><span begin="02:56.790" end="02:57.190">た</span><span begin="02:57.250" end="02:57.650">一</span><span begin="02:57.650" end="02:57.750">つ</span> <span begin="02:57.900" end="02:58.000">ま</span><span begin="02:58.070" end="02:58.470">た</span><span begin="02:58.520" end="02:58.920">一</span><span begin="02:58.940" end="02:59.000">つ</span> <span begin="02:59.160" end="02:59.780">灯</span><span begin="02:59.780" end="02:59.880">が</span><span begin="02:59.940" end="03:00.410">消</span><span begin="03:00.410" end="03:00.520">え</span><span begin="03:00.590" end="03:00.930">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">又一盏 又一盏 灯火熄灭了</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">又一盞 又一盞 燈火熄滅了</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">One by one again and again the lights went out</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">또 하나, 또 하나 등불이 꺼졌어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Encore une encore une une lumière s'est éteinte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Se apagó una luz y luego otra</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wieder eins und noch eins ein Licht ist erloschen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mais uma mais uma luz se apagou</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Еще один и еще один свет погас</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ancora una ancora una una luce si è spenta</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mata hitotsu mata hitotsu akari ga kieta</span></p>
      <p begin="03:01.210" end="03:06.560" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L27"><span begin="03:01.210" end="03:01.760">な</span><span begin="03:01.760" end="03:01.860">ん</span><span begin="03:01.860" end="03:02.130">て</span><span begin="03:02.470" end="03:03.000">愛</span><span begin="03:03.090" end="03:03.530">し</span><span begin="03:03.600" end="03:03.700">く</span><span begin="03:03.760" end="03:04.010">て</span><span begin="03:04.330" end="03:04.760">愚</span><span begin="03:04.830" end="03:05.150">か</span><span begin="03:05.180" end="03:05.450">な</span><span begin="03:05.490" end="03:06.560">の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">多么惹人怜爱 却又多么愚蠢啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">多麼惹人憐愛 卻又多麼愚蠢啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">How dear and foolish it is</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">얼마나 사랑스럽고 어리석은지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Comme c'est attachant et stupide</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Qué adorables y tontas somos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wie liebenswert und doch so töricht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Como somos amáveis e tolas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Как же это мило и как глупо</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quanto siamo preziosi e sciocchi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nante itoshikute oroka na no</span></p>
      <p begin="03:06.890" end="03:11.800" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L28"><span begin="03:06.890" end="03:07.280">声</span><span begin="03:07.380" end="03:07.600">無</span><span begin="03:07.710" end="03:07.940">き</span><span begin="03:08.020" end="03:08.350">声</span><span begin="03:08.350" end="03:08.580">を</span><span begin="03:08.650" end="03:08.920">聞</span><span begin="03:08.970" end="03:09.050">か</span><span begin="03:09.090" end="03:09.200">せ</span><span begin="03:09.280" end="03:11.800">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">让我听见那无声的声音吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">讓我聽見那無聲的聲音吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Let me hear the voiceless voice</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">소리 없는 목소리를 들려줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Laisse-moi entendre cette voix sans voix</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Déjame escuchar tu voz sin voz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lass mich deine stimmlose Stimme hören</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Deixe-me ouvir a voz sem voz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Дай мне услышать беззвучный голос</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Fammi sentire la tua voce senza voce</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Koenaki koe o kikasete</span></p>
      <p begin="03:13.370" end="03:16.290" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L29"><span begin="03:13.370" end="03:13.470">此</span><span begin="03:13.520" end="03:13.640">処</span><span begin="03:13.690" end="03:13.810">に</span><span begin="03:13.850" end="03:14.340">い</span><span begin="03:14.340" end="03:14.440">る</span><span begin="03:14.490" end="03:14.970">か</span><span begin="03:14.970" end="03:16.290">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">因为我就在这里</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">因為我就在這裡</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Because I am right here</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이곳에 있으니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Parce que je suis là</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Porque estoy aquí</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Denn ich bin hier</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Porque eu estou aqui</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Потому что я здесь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Perché sono qui</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Koko ni iru kara</span></p>
      <p begin="03:16.670" end="03:21.860" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L30"><span begin="03:16.670" end="03:17.040">嗚</span><span begin="03:17.040" end="03:17.930">呼</span><span begin="03:17.930" end="03:17.960">、</span><span begin="03:18.270" end="03:18.640">声</span><span begin="03:18.760" end="03:18.970">無</span><span begin="03:19.060" end="03:19.310">き</span><span begin="03:19.380" end="03:19.730">声</span><span begin="03:19.730" end="03:19.970">よ</span><span begin="03:20.010" end="03:20.490">響</span><span begin="03:20.490" end="03:20.600">い</span><span begin="03:20.670" end="03:21.860">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">啊 无声的声音啊 回荡起来吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">啊 無聲的聲音啊 迴盪起來吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ah, voiceless voice echo out</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아아, 소리 없는 목소리여 울려 퍼져라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ah que cette voix sans voix résonne</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ah, que resuene la voz sin voz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah oh stimmlose Stimme halle wider</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ah, ó voz sem voz, ressoe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ах беззвучный голос звучи эхом</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ah risuona o voce senza voce</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aa, koenaki koe yo hibiite</span></p>
    </div>
  </body>
</tt>
